{"tid":1569707,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於跳閘應唔應該繼續","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:35:07.000Z","uid":254898,"like":60,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"77747db98c0b07502038eeabe12430795e1ac8e3","tid":1569707,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"關於跳閘應唔應該繼續既問題<br />\n源於最近不斷有手足跳閘時<br />\n比藍絲謾罵，騷擾，甚至拍片<br />\n甚至傳有狗看守閘口一跳即捉<br />\n<br />\n咁就開始有人話：<br />\n其實跳閘會比人鬧破壞法治/失民心<br />\n跳閘風險好高等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實就好似之前被拍片對象講：<br />\n關你撚事咩！班藍絲廢老<br />\n做乜9都話架啦<br />\n而家都唔係塞地鐵阻人返工啦<br />\n根本完全冇影響正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班廢老唔敢跳就吠下咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跳閘實際只違反港鐵附例罰500<br />\n甚至有片見到捉到都唔罰比翻綠卡出添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyHVLw9-1k9A&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=08919442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A</a><br />\n洗乜比一班本來就唔識法治<br />\n唔講法治，維護警察，縱容制暴<br />\n雙重標準既人帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我並非跳閘發起人<br />\n但作為參與者，都係相信有用先去做<br />\n跳閘係要表達黨鐵頻頻封站<br />\n有意阻礙我地行動，但又試過封站期間開車比狗<br />\n甚至危急關頭停開列車<br />\n造成721，831等慘況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要既係到而家都未交出cctv<br />\n咁有咩理由促使我地停止跳閘"},{"pid":"06bbb2a012baeb293fc9652173637d34e49cafc2","tid":1569707,"uid":254898,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"咦終於擺脱左P牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3077b1910aa0f090693586a812aa67f3157828","tid":1569707,"uid":108337,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"跳閘係訓練自己既危機意識同應變能力<br />\n你要觀察現場環境安全而決定直接跳，換位跳定係唔跳<br />\n亦都要諗比人發現時用咩方法逃走<br />\n<br />\n但可惜好多人都係盲目咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f534ec618af96557e4c6a21dc7de1e840f5284","tid":1569707,"uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"跳出生活每一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65ff6590fa8bdc465857c61a36421587641720b","tid":1569707,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"無用, 只係表態<br />\n<br />\n我罷搭, 必須要用就會跳"},{"pid":"f457d45529a266784ecc32b691489269061b4c1d","tid":1569707,"uid":37922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f29f938e8b58235b3a32cbe0fd896ed9c7a99af","tid":1569707,"uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf3077b1910aa0f090693586a812aa67f3157828","tid":1569707,"uid":108337,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"跳閘係訓練自己既危機意識同應變能力<br />\n你要觀察現場環境安全而決定直接跳，換位跳定係唔跳<br />\n亦都要諗比人發現時用咩方法逃走<br />\n<br />\n但可惜好多人都係盲目咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"當然要注意安全，例如見到閘入面成隊狗望實都勇往直前，就等於送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0633345ffa008c165e923b88698b401ff920fc","tid":1569707,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d65ff6590fa8bdc465857c61a36421587641720b","tid":1569707,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"無用, 只係表態<br />\n<br />\n我罷搭, 必須要用就會跳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"個point就係錯果個唔係我地，如果明明mtr快D既就冇必要搵其他方法達到罷搭，有少少好似避佢咁。無可否認香港係需要mtr，所以我地唔係要否定呢個交通工具，我地係想否定佢管理層作出既行為，例如之前封站/乃至而家都未交出cctv。"},{"pid":"e14d62c47ff28ef0da2a3bc119bae551230f67fd